ydj-s09nxHoGdEGy1TphipvA5w&oe=676BF5FE"}, {"file_name": "SS4.png", "id": "1668334477232970", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974841_1668334480566303_7727439569636657572_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=oAkCdQyLALEQ7kNvgECWNzu&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAodh9ZGX_-G81oe2V1iWuvD6e_rk1Zq4xgn1kVSiDzKQ&oe=676BD937"}, {"file_name": "SS5.png", "id": "1213062970013122", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982495_1213062973346455_3756223896267353315_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=TpxvFX7QMI0Q7kNvgFss26h&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDQblyz2fclaSUmuZvOD9-rrDv8ZiiXuCxlmW7sVyGITA&oe=676C0202"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Haunted Exit Escape Room - Horror Games", "keywords": ["Horror", "Scary", "Haunted", "Granny", "Fear"], "long_description": "Welcome to Haunted Escape, a VR experience that\u2019ll keep you on the edge of your seat! You\u2019ve got one goal: escape the haunted room before the creepy inhabitants get to you. Solve puzzles, avoid terrifying creatures, and make it out alive.\n\nIn Haunted Escape, you\u2019ll encounter some seriously spooky characters\u2014like a Zombie Dog, a dead Joker, and even an eerie Mummy. Each challenge will test your nerves and your puzzle-solving skills. The best part? You can play it alone or with a friend!\n\nThe game offers two modes:\n- Solo Mode: It\u2019s just you against the haunted room\u2014get out before it\u2019s too late!\n- Co-op Mode: Work with a friend to help each other escape. Can you both survive?\n\nKey Features:\n- Play solo or team up in co-op mode.\n- Face off against creepy creatures like Granny, Ghosts, a Zombie Dog, and more.\n- High-quality VR graphics for an immersive, hair-raising experience.\n- Puzzles that challenge your brain while keeping your heart racing.\n- Exclusively available on Oculus Quest.", "short_description": "Ge